about: I am Rahul Kumar, a passionate developer with expertise in MERN stack, Python, and Java, focused on creating impactful and user-friendly applications.
I have completed a certified internship at EY GDS & AICTE, gaining hands-on experience in full-stack development, REST API integration, and deployment.
My projects include an AI-powered Resume Screening System and a Food Delivery App, showcasing my skills in both AI and modern web technologies.
I believe in continuous learning, adaptability, and teamwork, which drive me to deliver high-quality solutions.
Beyond coding, I enjoy exploring emerging technologies, AI trends, and innovative ideas that merge technology with real-world impact.
